Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Frida Server Not Running
# Check if Frida server is running
adb shell ps | grep frida-server

# Restart Frida server
adb shell "su -c 'killall frida-server'"
adb shell "su -c '/data/local/tmp/frida-server &'"
Issue: Application Crashes on Hook
Cause: Incorrect method signature or class name
Solution: Use frida-trace to identify correct signatures
Command: frida-trace -U -f com.example.pinningtest -j '*!*check*/i'
Issue: No Traffic in Burp Suite
Verify proxy settings: adb shell settings get global http_proxy
Check certificate installation: Ensure Burp CA cert is installed
Restart application: Some apps cache proxy settings
Issue: Script Injection Fails
Check package name: Verify with adb shell pm list packages
Verify device connection: Run frida-ps -U
Check for anti-Frida: Some apps detect Frida; try obfuscation techniques
